325
00:25:24,380 --> 00:25:25,380
ha?

326
00:26:15,320 --> 00:26:17,440
(Preview ng Panghuling Episode)
Sa sandaling malabo at nag-aalinlangan,

327
00:26:17,920 --> 00:26:19,690
